ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝有心巴打回覆<br />\n<br />\n我唯有乖乖等下次開</blockquote><br />\n早啲問佢幾時有貨返、拎張卡片、好似追數佬咁打去就得咖啦<br />\n或者多啲幫襯佢地，打好關係就乜都留比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f049148e0b7b91016c52a73a369c7b1eea313e42","tid":105513,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔買最好 等ps5<br />\n買左你實後悔</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一出ps5 會冇game 玩，等slim 先</blockquote><br />\n出slim既同時會公佈ps5 pro, 到時d games唔用pro玩一定大cut畫質/frame rate，所以最好等埋ps5 pro"}]}